data.description: Beautifully updated 1-story home in highly desired Teas Lakes! Sellers made more than $23,000 in upgrades. Plenty of room including 3 bedrooms, 2 full bathrooms, formal dining, and a study/office off of the primary bedroom! Flooring includes newly added vinyl plank flooring, carpet, wood and tile. Kitchen was updated with granite countertops and new electric stove/oven. New countertop in bathroom. Deck added in back to create a perfect outdoor space for guests, parties. Newly added recessed lighting. Exterior offers attached garage, patio and a fully fenced backyard that's great for kids, pets. Low Tax Rate!
